messages.subject: Re: Anniversary of this group
messages.msgSnippet: Sandra, I love this post. Makes me smile. Thank you for this group and for many years of inspiration. I still follow along, listen in and learn. I ve learned
messages.messageBody:
Sandra, 

I love this post. Makes me smile. Thank you for this group and for many years of inspiration. I still follow along, listen in and learn. I've learned so much. Thank you. 

With gratitude, 
Jen 



---In AlwaysLearning@yahoogroups.com, <Sandra@...> wrote :

Facebook showed me this:


Sandra Dodd
November 24, 2013 at 9:58pm · 
The anniversary of a project: The Always Learning discussion at yahoogroups is twelve years old today, and still going strong. 72,622 messages so far.  Pam Sorooshian and Joyce Kurtak Fetteroll have helped me with it from the beginning. The first post was by Deb Lewis. Thank you, and all those who've participated in that time, many people have been helped, and I appreciate the assistance from so many people who came and stayed a while or the whole time. 

So sixteen years of this group.  It has slowed down, but it’s still here! :-)

Sandra
